<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    @page { size: A4; margin: 2.5cm 2.5cm; }
    body { font-family: "DejaVu Sans", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; color: #1a1a1a; line-height: 1.8; }
    h1 { font-size: 15pt; text-align: center; color: #1e3a5f; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .subtitle { text-align: center; color: #555; font-size: 9pt; margin-bottom: 30px; }
    hr { border: none; border-top: 2px solid #1e3a5f; margin: 16px 0 24px 0; }
    .section { margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .section-title { font-weight: bold; font-size: 10pt; color: #1e3a5f; margin-bottom: 8px; text-decoration: underline; }
    .info-row { display: flex; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .info-label { width: 180px; flex-shrink: 0; color: #555; }
    .info-value { font-weight: 500; }
    .amount-box {
      background: #f0f4f8;
      border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      margin: 16px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .amount-label { font-size: 9pt; color: #64748b; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .amount-value { font-size: 20pt; font-weight: bold; color: #1e3a5f; }
    .signature { margin-top: 50px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; }
    .sign-box { width: 200px; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; min-height: 80px; font-size: 9pt; }
    .legal { font-size: 8pt; color: #888; margin-top: 30px; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding-top: 8px; text-align: center; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <h1>Attestation de loyer</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">À destination de la Caisse d'Allocations Familiales (CAF)</p>
  <hr>

  <p>Je soussigné(e), bailleur du logement désigné ci-dessous, atteste sur l'honneur que :</p>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">Informations sur le logement</div>
    <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">Adresse :</span><span class="info-value">{{ property_address }}</span></div>
    <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">Logement :</span><span class="info-value">{{ unit_ref }} ({{ unit_type }})</span></div>
    {% if area_sqm %}<div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">Surface :</span><span class="info-value">{{ area_sqm }} m²</span></div>{% endif %}
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">Informations sur le locataire</div>
    <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">Nom :</span><span class="info-value">{{ tenant_name }}</span></div>
    {% if tenant_birth_date %}<div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">Date de naissance :</span><span class="info-value">{{ tenant_birth_date }}</span></div>{% endif %}
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">Informations sur le bail</div>
    <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">Date d'entrée :</span><span class="info-value">{{ start_date }}</span></div>
    <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">Type de bail :</span><span class="info-value">{{ lease_type_label }}</span></div>
    <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">Statut :</span><span class="info-value">{{ 'Bail en cours' if is_active else 'Bail résilié' }}</span></div>
  </div>

  <div class="amount-box">
    <div class="amount-label">Montant mensuel du loyer (charges comprises)</div>
    <div class="amount-value">{{ total_monthly }} €</div>
    <div style="font-size: 9pt; color: #555; margin-top: 6px;">
      Loyer HC : {{ rent_amount }} € &nbsp;|&nbsp; Charges : {{ charges_amount }} €
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="signature">
    <div>
      <p style="font-size: 9pt; color: #555;">Fait à :</p>
      <p>______________________________</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p style="font-size: 9pt; color: #555;">Le :</p>
      <p>______________________________</p>
    </div>
    <div class="sign-box">
      <p style="font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 8px;">Signature du bailleur</p>
      <br><br>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="legal">
    Document généré par Locataire Cloud &bull; Cette attestation est fournie à titre indicatif. Le bailleur certifie l'exactitude des informations.
  </div>

</body>
</html>
